    },
    {
      "id": "bsky_joshmatlow.bsky.social_3mn7vgnpou226",
      "text": "Too many renters in Toronto are overheating in their own homes. And year after year, they’ve asked city hall for action. It’s time to move forward with a Maximum Temperature By-law to protect the health and safety of our city’s tenants. www.cbc.ca/news/canada/...",
