    {
      "id": "bsky_coteau.bsky.social_3lhya4kruss27",
      "text": "Went out canvassing for Andrea Hazell in Scarborough-Guildwood! She’s got a fantastic team working hard to connect with voters. If you can, come out and help—every conversation counts! #TeamHazel #ScarboroughGuildwood #OnPoli @AndreaHazelll",
      "author": "Michael Coteau",
      "handle": "coteau.bsky.social",
      "likes": 0,
      "retweets": 0,
      "created_utc": 1739365202,
      "permalink": "https://bsky.app/profile/coteau.bsky.social/post/3lhya4kruss27",
      "source": "bluesky"
    },
    {
      "id": "bsky_coteau.bsky.social_3lhrapglt5222",
      "text": "Happy to support @QadiraJackson as she runs to be the next MPP for Scarborough Southwest! Her passion, dedication, and commitment to the community are exactly what’s needed at Queen’s Park. Honoured to speak at her fundraiser—let’s get her elected! #onpoli #TeamQadira",
      "author": "Michael Coteau",
      "handle": "coteau.bsky.social",
      "likes": 0,
      "retweets": 0,
      "created_utc": 1739125317,
      "permalink": "https://bsky.app/profile/coteau.bsky.social/post/3lhrapglt5222",
      "source": "bluesky"
    },
    {
      "id": "bsky_coteau.bsky.social_3lhqynqlbb226",
      "text": "Great to join Andrea Hazell in Scarborough-Guildwood as she runs for re-election as MPP! Andrea brings the kind of energy needed at Queen’s Park to amplify the voices and concerns of her constituents. Looking forward to seeing her continue to deliver for the community! #onpoli @AndreaHazelll",
      "author": "Michael Coteau",
      "handle": "coteau.bsky.social",
      "likes": 0,
      "retweets": 0,
      "created_utc": 1739116671,
      "permalink": "https://bsky.app/profile/coteau.bsky.social/post/3lhqynqlbb226",
      "source": "bluesky"
    },
    {
      "id": "bsky_coteau.bsky.social_3lhlq2hjjgc2s",
      "text": "Great attending the Toronto Educational Opportunity Fund Lunar New Year event to help raise money for student nutrition programs. Thank you, Toronto Education Workers/Local 4400, for your dedication to students. Always great seeing everyone! #StudentNutrition #TOpoli",
      "author": "Michael Coteau",
      "handle": "coteau.bsky.social",
      "likes": 0,
      "retweets": 0,
      "created_utc": 1738935635,
      "permalink": "https://bsky.app/profile/coteau.bsky.social/post/3lhlq2hjjgc2s",
      "source": "bluesky"
    },
    {
      "id": "bsky_coteau.bsky.social_3lcyskaglas2k",
      "text": "Mike Harris’s cuts to social services, housing, and healthcare pushed Ontario’s most vulnerable deeper into crisis. Pierre Poilievre is singing the same tune: tax cuts for the rich, austerity for the rest. We can’t afford another era of cruel, short-sighted policies. #cdnpoli",
      "author": "Michael Coteau",
      "handle": "coteau.bsky.social",
      "likes": 0,
      "retweets": 0,
      "created_utc": 1733887430,
      "permalink": "https://bsky.app/profile/coteau.bsky.social/post/3lcyskaglas2k",
      "source": "bluesky"
    },
    {
      "id": "bsky_coteau.bsky.social_3lcysjumtec2k",
      "text": "Pierre Poilievre’s playbook feels eerily familiar: tax cuts for the wealthy, slashing public services, and a ‘common sense’ branding. Looks like he’s channeling Mike Harris’s divisive and damaging legacy. We’ve seen this movie before, and we know how it ends. #cdnpoli",
      "author": "Michael Coteau",
      "handle": "coteau.bsky.social",
      "likes": 0,
      "retweets": 0,
      "created_utc": 1733887418,
      "permalink": "https://bsky.app/profile/coteau.bsky.social/post/3lcysjumtec2k",
